    "question": "If a bucket contains 4 ounces of sand and 16 ounces of water, how many ounces of water would need to evaporate in order to make the ratio of the number of ounces of sand to the number of ounces of water 2 to 3?",
    "options": {
      "A": "6",
      "B": "7",
      "C": "8",
      "D": "10"
    },
